OL,3,CWhy does the King think we live in
OL,4,C'deeply troubling' times?
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FKing Charles ended his message by
OL,12,Frenewing his "own pledge of duty and
OL,13,Fservice to you all", just as he mother
OL,14,Fhad done before him.
OL,16,FBritain will soon have a new national
OL,17,Fmemorial to Queen Elizabeth in London,
OL,18,Fmuch like Americans honour their past
OL,19,Fpresidents in Washington DC.
OL,26,@tD@NOUuD@SO]
