OL,3,CWhy does the King think we live in
OL,4,C'deeply troubling' times?
OL,6,FNo British monarch can match her seven
OL,7,Fdecade-long reign, and therefore the
OL,8,Fdate of Queen Elizabeth's birth has
OL,9,Fearned its place in the history books.
OL,11,FThis is the Talking Royals - our
OL,12,Fweekly podcast about the Royal Family,
OL,13,Fwith ITV News Royal Editor Chris Ship
OL,14,Fand Producer Lizzie Robinson.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/12
